The Animation How To's provide several step-by-step examples of working with and using the different [](Engine\Animation\Persona\Modes) within Unreal Engine 4. 
Whether you are new to animation in Unreal Engine 4 or want to learn how to work with the different tools, the How To pages below cover a broad range of topics and aim to give you a place to start or expand upon your current knowledge. 

